conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Hi, my name is Alex and I'm reaching out from DeepData AI. We're a data processing solution that helps companies like yours streamline their data workflow and gain valuable insights. I came across your company and noticed you're using Calendly for appointment scheduling. How are you currently handling your data processing needs?

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: Ah, yeah. We're using a combination of in-house tools and some third-party services. It's been working okay so far, but we're always looking for ways to improve. What makes DeepData AI different from what's already out there?

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Well, our AI-powered engine can handle large volumes of data quickly and accurately, and our integration with popular tools like Google Suite and Microsoft makes it easy to incorporate into your existing workflow. We've seen companies like yours reduce their data processing time by up to 50%. Would you like to hear more about how it works?

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: That sounds interesting, but I have to say, we're pretty happy with our current setup. What kind of pricing are we talking about here? We're a large company, so we'd need a solution that can scale with us.

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Our pricing varies depending on the size of the company and the specific needs of the project. For a company of your size, we'd likely be looking at a custom enterprise plan, which starts at around $50,000 per year. But like I said, we've seen companies like yours achieve significant ROI through improved efficiency and accuracy.

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: That's a bit steeper than I was expecting. We've also been talking to some of your competitors, like Tableau and Power BI, and their pricing seems more in line with what we're looking for. Can you tell me what sets DeepData AI apart from those solutions?

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Absolutely. While those solutions are certainly capable, they often require a lot of manual configuration and maintenance. Our AI-powered engine automates a lot of that process, saving you time and resources in the long run. Plus, our customer support team is available 24/7 to help with any issues that may arise.

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: I appreciate the pitch, but to be honest, the price is just too high for us. We're not convinced that the benefits outweigh the cost, especially when compared to some of the other options out there. I think we're going to have to pass on DeepData AI for now.
